    <p>The Office of the Vice-President, Research and Innovation is an invaluable resource during all stages of the grant process. Ensure you connect&nbsp;with the right <a href="/content/ryerson/research/contact/" target="_blank">Grants/Contracts Officer or Applied Research and Innovation Advisor<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a>.</p>
    





