                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1549040064440-3--familiarize-yourself-with-the-application-form-and-selection-criteria" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1549040064440-3--familiarize-yourself-with-the-application-form-and-selection-criteria" aria-controls="accordion-content-1549040064440-3--familiarize-yourself-with-the-application-form-and-selection-criteria" aria-expanded="false">
                            3. Familiarize yourself with the application form and selection criteria
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1549040064440-3--familiarize-yourself-with-the-application-form-and-selection-criteria" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1549040064440-3--familiarize-yourself-with-the-application-form-and-selection-criteria">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1549040064440 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="d747228d-1181-4034-b742-76d398a830cd" >

    <p>Carefully read the guidelines provided and program descriptions. These guidelines are normally updated every year, and are generally available on the website of the granting agency.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#d747228d-1181-4034-b742-76d398a830cd");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1549040064463-4--use-language-the-grant-agency-uses-and-understand-their-research-priorities" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1549040064463-4--use-language-the-grant-agency-uses-and-understand-their-research-priorities" aria-controls="accordion-content-1549040064463-4--use-language-the-grant-agency-uses-and-understand-their-research-priorities" aria-expanded="false">
                            4. Use language the grant agency uses and understand their research priorities
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1549040064463-4--use-language-the-grant-agency-uses-and-understand-their-research-priorities" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1549040064463-4--use-language-the-grant-agency-uses-and-understand-their-research-priorities">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1549040064463 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="896a2c1f-0ce4-4bf8-9df2-3ca9031188de" >

    <p>Identify the knowledge gap or problem that needs to be solved. Also identify the knowledge users. Explain how your research program or project is expected to (1) solve a problem or fill a knowledge gap, and (2) benefit knowledge users. Make sure to define outcomes and deliverables, and set your expectations and limitations. Highlight your achievements and contributions that are relevant to the proposed research. Keep in mind that <a href="/content/ryerson/research/resources/km/" target="_blank">Knowledge Mobilization<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a>&nbsp;as well as&nbsp;<a href="/content/ryerson/research/resources/commercialization/" target="_blank">Technology Transfer and Intellectual Property<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a> activities may also be important aspects of your grant development.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#896a2c1f-0ce4-4bf8-9df2-3ca9031188de");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h2 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1549040064486-5--prepare-your-grant-authorization-form--gaf--and-upload-relevant-documents" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1549040064486-5--prepare-your-grant-authorization-form--gaf--and-upload-relevant-documents" aria-controls="accordion-content-1549040064486-5--prepare-your-grant-authorization-form--gaf--and-upload-relevant-documents" aria-expanded="false">
                            5. Prepare your Grant Authorization Form (GAF) and upload relevant documents
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1549040064486-5--prepare-your-grant-authorization-form--gaf--and-upload-relevant-documents" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1549040064486-5--prepare-your-grant-authorization-form--gaf--and-upload-relevant-documents">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1549040064486 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="fc10901c-3e84-4f64-a584-df6f751925b9" >

    <p>The GAF is in RIS - our database with all the information on grants and applications. RIS is mandatory for all grant applications. <a href="https://cas.ryerson.ca/login?service=https://ccs.cf.ryerson.ca/researchGrant/casAuthentication/cas_authorisation.cfm" target="_blank">Log in to RIS<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a>.</p>
    





